    Package Description
    org.glassfish.jersey.server.wadl.internal.generators.resourcedoc
    Jersey server-side WADL internal classes supporting generation of resource documentation with wadl generators.
    org.glassfish.jersey.server.wadl.internal.generators.resourcedoc.model
    Jersey server-side WADL internal JAXB beans used for generation of resource documentation with wadl generators.
    org.glassfish.jersey.wadl.doclet
    Jersey classes used for doclet generation for WADL purposes.
